## Paid Amplification Playbook

### TikTok Spark Ads (Primary Paid Channel)

- **When to boost**: Organic post hits 1K+ views in first 24 hours
- **Budget**: $20-50/day for 3-5 day bursts (NOT continuous daily)
- **Strategy**: 2-3 boost cycles per month. Boost winners, kill losers.
- **Setup**: TikTok Ads Manager > Spark Ads > authorize your organic post > set budget
- **Kill criteria**: CPC > $0.50 after $20 spend = stop. CPM > $12 = stop.
- **Engagement persistence**: Likes earned on Spark Ads stay permanently on the organic post

### Meta/Instagram Boost (Secondary)

- **When to boost**: Reel reaches 500+ organic views
- **Budget**: $10-30/day for 2-3 day bursts
- **Targeting**: 18-30, interests: personal finance, taxes, budgeting, investing
- **Retargeting**: Create custom audience from TikTok pixel + website visitors
- **Kill criteria**: CPC > $1.00 after $15 spend = stop

### Budget Reality

At $200-500/mo total ad spend, you run ads ~10-17 days/month (not continuously). TikTok minimum is $20/day per ad group. This aligns with the "boost winners" approach — you don't need daily ads, you need concentrated bursts on proven content.

## Analytics Framework (Weekly Review)

Every Monday, review these metrics in Postiz analytics:

### Per Platform
- **TikTok**: Views, completion rate, profile visits, followers gained
- **Instagram**: Reach, saves, shares, profile visits
- **X**: Impressions, quote tweets, profile clicks, followers
- **YouTube**: Views, subscriber conversions, watch time

### Content Performance
- Top 3 posts by engagement — what format/topic/hook worked?
- Bottom 3 posts — what flopped and why?
- Which pillar is performing best this week?

### Action Items
- Double down on winning format/topic next week
- Kill underperforming content type
- Identify next Spark Ad candidate (top organic post)
- Adjust posting times based on when views peak

## Creator Outreach

### Target Profile
- Personal finance micro-influencers: 10K-100K followers
- Platforms: TikTok and Instagram primarily
- Style: Authentic, educational, Gen Z native (not corporate)
- Examples: tax TikTokers, "adulting" creators, financial literacy educators

### DM Template
"Hey [name]! I built FileFree — a completely free tax filing app (no hidden fees, no data selling). I'd love for you to try it and share your honest reaction. No script, just scan your W-2 and see what happens. Interested?"

### Partnership Terms
- **Option A** (preferred): Free product + rev share on referral signups (track via UTM codes)
- **Option B**: Flat fee $50-200 per post (only for creators with proven engagement rates > 5%)
- Track all partnerships with UTM links: `filefree.tax?utm_source=tiktok&utm_medium=creator&utm_campaign=[creator_name]`

